## Building the aplication
1. Go to the aplication folder
2. Grant "make" permissions for execution (may not be necessary): `$ chmod +x make` 
3. Run it: `$ ./make`

## Running
1. Go to the created folder (Operation)
2. Run rmiregistry in background: `$ rmiregistry &`
3. Run server: `$ java OperationServer`
4. Run client: `$ java OperationClient [host]`
5. Follow application instructions :)
